snippet.title: SONG of IRON Trailer #2  ( 4k, 60fps )
snippet.description:
Wish-list Song of Iron on steam! https://tinyurl.com/wishlist-song-of-Iron

Behind you lies a trail of broken helms, shattered shields. You hold the axe of a fallen foe. Worn and dented, it will suit it's purpose. What lies ahead is still a mystery.

I had a lot of fun putting this trailer together and am excited to show off the new locations, new enemies and new abilities! 

Song of Iron is coming to Xbox and PC later this year
Consider Subscribing! - https://tinyurl.com/Sub-to-Song-of-Iron

---Join the Song of Iron party!---
